actionConfiguration.body:
select 
TO_CHAR(c.created_time,'YYYY-MM-DD') AS created_time,
c.created_by,
c.retailer_code,
c.cashback_status,
c.lead_source_type,
cp.partner_id,
cp.channel_partner_name,
c.phone_number,
c.asm_name,
c.remarks,
c.ho_remarks,
c.ho_updated_by,
c.asm_remarks,
c.asm_updated_by,
c.cashback_amount,
c.bank_account_name,
c.bank_account_number,
c.bank_name,
c.ifsc_code,
TO_CHAR(c.updated_time,'YYYY-MM-DD') AS updated_time,
c.lead_given_by,
c.cashback_id,
c.accounts_updated_by,
c.transaction_id,
c.transaction_date,
c.accounts_remarks
from cashback as c
left join channel_partners as cp on cp.partner_id=c.partner_id
where cashback_status not in ('OPEN','NOT_APPROVED_HO','NOT_APPROVED_ASM','APPROVED_BY_HO')
order by cashback_id desc
